{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1015_00_01","textHome":"我叫环忧，其实才刚刚成为魔法少女。@还有，因为一直住院，有很多事情不太懂。@可能会多麻烦你，希望你不要介意。@啊，其实我的姐姐也是魔法少女来着，@下次介绍给你哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101500}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1015_00_17","textHome":"虽然我看上去很开朗阳光，@但住院的时候还是哭了很多次……@但是，不要告诉姐姐哦。@总感觉她也会伤心的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":101500,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1015_00_18","textHome":"虽然只是些许，但我感受到了。@姐姐在学校，好像也有很多难事。@但我不说，这件事就藏在我心里吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101500}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":